title: The Problem With Investing Culture Trends (Hour 1)
description:
George Kamel & Rachel Cruze discuss:

How to save for kids college,

What to do after moving out of your parents' house,

How sinking funds work,

The danger of investing culture,

Preparing for retirement early in life.
